  "description": "<p>Reach for the Choucas Light harness for fast and light missions \u2013 one of the world's lightest. The minimalist design and lightweight materials pair with two tie-in loops and a unique leg loop system. A completely openable design allows you to put it on or taken it off with your feet on the ground, so you don't need to remove your skis or crampons.</p><ul><li>UHMW polyethylene webbing and nylon attachment points are incredibly lightweight and abrasion-resistant</li><li>Two tie-in points and adjustable clip in place of traditional belay loop</li><li>Leg loops secure with low-profile aluminum buckle and webbing</li><li>2 minimalist gear loops handle a few carabiners each</li><li>Each leg loops features an ice-screw holder for quick access</li><li>Harness can be donned while wearing skis or crampons</li><li>Includes protective carrying bag</li></ul>",
